WEBVTT

00:19.360 --> 00:23.240
VIII. INTUITION OR GUIDANCE.

00:23.240 --> 00:29.460
In all thy ways acknowledge him, and he shall direct thy paths.

00:30.760 --> 00:36.700
There is nothing too great of accomplishment for the man who knows the power of his word,

00:36.940 --> 00:43.700
and who follows his intuitive leads. By the word he starts in action unseen forces,

00:44.080 --> 00:51.960
and can rebuild his body or remould his affairs. It is therefore of the utmost importance to choose

00:51.960 --> 00:57.580
the right words, and the student carefully selects the affirmation he wishes to catapult

00:57.580 --> 01:05.120
into the invisible. He knows that God is his supply, and that there is a supply for every demand,

01:05.500 --> 01:11.660
and that his spoken word releases this supply. Ask, and ye shall receive.

01:12.960 --> 01:19.740
Man must make the first move. Draw nigh to God, and he will draw nigh to you.

01:20.540 --> 01:26.200
I have often been asked just how to make a demonstration. I reply,

01:26.800 --> 01:34.100
Speak the word, and then do not do anything until you get a definite lead. Demand the lead, saying,

01:34.720 --> 01:40.420
Infinite spirit, reveal to me the way, let me know if there's anything for me to do.

01:41.480 --> 01:46.860
The answer will come through intuition, or hunch, a chance remark from someone,

01:46.860 --> 01:54.880
or a passage in a book, etc. etc. The answers are sometimes quite startling in their exactness.

01:55.060 --> 02:01.460
For example, a woman desired a large sum of money. She spoke the words, Infinite spirit,

02:01.820 --> 02:08.280
open the way for my immediate supply, let all that is mine by divine right now reach me in

02:08.280 --> 02:15.120
great avalanches of abundance. Then she added, Give me a definite lead, let me know if there

02:15.120 --> 02:21.840
is anything for me to do. The thought came quickly. Give a certain friend, who had helped

02:21.840 --> 02:28.280
her spiritually, a hundred dollars. She told her friend, who said, Wait and get another lead

02:28.280 --> 02:35.340
before giving it. So she waited, and that day met a woman who said to her, I gave someone a dollar

02:35.340 --> 02:43.600
today. It was just as much for me as it would be for you to give someone a hundred. This was indeed

02:43.600 --> 02:50.380
an unmistakable lead, so she knew she was right in giving the hundred dollars. It was a gift which

02:50.380 --> 02:56.220
proved a great investment for shortly after that, a large sum of money came to her in a remarkable

02:56.220 --> 03:04.380
way. Giving opens the way for receiving. In order to create activity in finances, one should give.

03:05.200 --> 03:12.380
Tithing, or giving one tenth of one's income, is an old Jewish custom and is sure to bring increase.

03:13.180 --> 03:19.480
Many of the richest men in the country have been tithers and have never known it to fail as an

03:19.480 --> 03:26.940
investment. The tenth part goes forth and returns blessed and multiplied, but the gift or tithe must

03:26.940 --> 03:34.240
be given with love and cheerfulness, for God loveth a cheerful giver. Bills should be paid

03:34.240 --> 03:40.600
cheerfully. All money should be sent forth fearlessly and with a blessing. This attitude

03:40.600 --> 03:49.320
of mind makes man master of money. It is his to obey, and his spoken word then opens vast reservoirs

03:49.320 --> 03:57.540
of wealth. Man himself limits his supply by his limited vision. Sometimes the student has a great

03:57.540 --> 04:04.280
realization of wealth, but is afraid to act. The vision and action must go hand in hand,

04:04.280 --> 04:07.640
as in the case of the man who bought the fur-lined overcoat.

04:08.720 --> 04:15.040
A woman came to me asking me to speak the word for a position, so I demanded,

04:15.620 --> 04:23.900
Infinite Spirit, open the way for this woman's right position. Never ask for just a position.

04:24.440 --> 04:31.660
Ask for the right position, the place already planned in divine mind, as it is the only one

04:31.660 --> 04:38.560
will give satisfaction. I then gave thanks that she had already received, and that it would

04:38.560 --> 04:45.640
manifest quickly. Very soon she had three positions offered her, two in New York and

04:45.640 --> 04:52.880
one in Palm Beach, and she did not know which one to choose. I said, ask for a definite lead.

04:53.960 --> 04:59.120
The time was almost up and was still undecided when one day she telephoned,

04:59.120 --> 05:06.640
When I woke up this morning I could smell Palm Beach. She had been there before and knew its

05:06.640 --> 05:13.100
balmy fragrance. I replied, well if you can smell Palm Beach from here, it's certainly your lead.

05:14.180 --> 05:20.540
She accepted the position and it proved a great success. Often one's lead comes at an unexpected

05:20.540 --> 05:27.860
time. One day I was walking down the street when suddenly I felt a strong urge to go to a certain

05:27.860 --> 05:34.280
bakery a block or two away. The reasoning mind resisted, arguing, there is nothing there that

05:34.280 --> 05:41.740
you want. However, I had learned not to reason, so I went to the bakery, looked at everything,

05:41.960 --> 05:47.600
and there was certainly nothing there that I wanted. But coming out, I encountered a woman

05:47.600 --> 05:52.400
I had thought of often, and who was in great need of the help which I could give her.

05:52.400 --> 05:57.140
So often, one goes for one thing and finds another.

05:58.920 --> 06:06.700
Intuition is a spiritual faculty and does not explain, but simply points the way. A person

06:06.700 --> 06:14.940
often receives a lead during a treatment. The idea that comes may seem quite irrelevant, but

06:14.940 --> 06:18.240
some of God's leadings are mysterious.

06:20.220 --> 06:26.520
In the class one day, I was treating that each individual would receive a definite lead.

06:27.240 --> 06:31.060
A woman came to me afterwards and said, while you were treating,

06:31.220 --> 06:34.740
I got the hunch to take my furniture out of storage and get an apartment.

06:35.740 --> 06:41.240
The woman had come to be treated for health. I told her I knew in getting a home of her own,

06:41.240 --> 06:46.760
her health would improve, and I added, I believe your trouble, which is a congestion,

06:47.180 --> 06:54.000
has come from having things stored away. Congestion of things causes congestion in the body.

06:54.720 --> 06:58.860
You have violated the law of use, and your body is paying the penalty.

06:59.820 --> 07:06.340
So I gave thanks that divine order was established in her mind, body and affairs.

07:07.120 --> 07:13.460
People little dream of how their affairs react on the body. There is a mental correspondence

07:13.460 --> 07:19.480
for every disease. A person might receive instantaneous healing through the realization

07:19.480 --> 07:25.780
of his body being a perfect idea in divine mind and therefore whole and perfect, but if he

07:25.780 --> 07:33.920
continues his destructive thinking, hoarding, hating, fearing, condemning, the disease will return.

07:34.740 --> 07:42.220
Jesus Christ knew that all sickness came from sin, but admonished the leper after the healing

07:42.740 --> 07:51.160
to go and sin no more, lest a worse thing come upon him. So man's soul, or subconscious mind,

07:51.700 --> 07:59.480
must be washed whiter than snow for permanent healing, and the metaphysician is always delving

07:59.480 --> 08:08.420
deep for the correspondence. Jesus Christ said, condemn not, lest ye also be condemned.

08:09.780 --> 08:18.000
Judge not, lest ye be judged. Many people have attracted disease and unhappiness through the

08:18.000 --> 08:26.980
condemnation of others. What man condemns in others, he attracts to himself. For example,

08:26.980 --> 08:33.420
a friend came to me in anger and distress because her husband had deserted her for another woman.

08:34.180 --> 08:37.180
She condemned the other woman and said continually,

08:37.920 --> 08:42.860
she knew he was a married man, she had no right to accept his attentions.

08:44.000 --> 08:50.860
I replied, stop condemning the woman, bless her, and be through with the situation, otherwise you

08:50.860 --> 08:57.620
are attracting the same thing to yourself. She was deaf to my words, and a year or two later

08:57.620 --> 09:05.620
became deeply interested in a married man herself. Man picks up a live wire whenever he criticizes

09:05.620 --> 09:14.280
or condemns, and may expect a shock. Indecision is a stumbling block in many a pathway. In order

09:14.280 --> 09:22.140
to overcome it, make the statement repeatedly, I am always under direct inspiration. I make

09:22.140 --> 09:29.880
right decisions quickly. These words impress the subconscious, and soon one finds himself

09:29.880 --> 09:37.240
awake and alert, making his right moves without hesitation. I have found it destructive to look

09:37.240 --> 09:44.660
the psychic plane for guidance, as it is the plane of many minds, and not the one mind.

09:45.440 --> 09:51.780
As man opens his mind to subjectivity, he becomes a target for destructive forces.

09:52.300 --> 09:59.860
The psychic plane is the result of man's mortal thought, and is on the plane of opposites. He may

09:59.860 --> 10:07.920
receive either good or bad messages. The science of numbers and the reading of horoscopes keep man

10:07.920 --> 10:16.000
down the mental or mortal plane, for they deal only with the karmic path. I know of a man who

10:16.000 --> 10:22.800
should have been dead years ago according to his horoscope, but he is alive and a leader of one of

10:22.800 --> 10:30.580
the biggest movements in this country for the uplift of humanity. It takes a very strong mind

10:30.580 --> 10:35.260
to neutralize a prophecy of evil. The student should declare,

10:36.080 --> 10:43.280
Every false prophecy shall come to naught. Every plan my Father in heaven has not planned

10:43.280 --> 10:52.600
shall be dissolved and dissipated. The divine idea now comes to pass. However, if any good message

10:52.600 --> 11:00.640
has ever been given one of coming happiness or wealth, harbor and expect it, and it will manifest

11:00.640 --> 11:08.240
sooner or later through the law of expectancy. Man's will should be used to back the universal will.

11:08.820 --> 11:16.220
I will that the will of God be done. It is God's will to give every man

11:16.220 --> 11:22.280
every righteous desire of his heart, and man's will should be used to hold the perfect vision.

11:22.280 --> 11:29.700
Without wavering, the prodigal son said, I will arise and go to my Father.

11:31.080 --> 11:36.660
It is indeed often an effort of the will to leave the husks and swine of mortal thinking.

11:37.300 --> 11:44.680
It is so much easier for the average person to have fear than faith. So faith is an effort of the

11:44.680 --> 11:44.980
will.

11:46.000 --> 11:52.460
As man becomes spiritually awakened, he recognizes that any external inharmony is

11:52.460 --> 11:59.320
the correspondence of mental inharmony. If he stumbles or falls, he may know he is stumbling

11:59.320 --> 12:06.300
or falling in consciousness. One day a student was walking along the street, condemning someone

12:06.300 --> 12:12.700
in her thoughts. She was saying mentally, that woman is the most disagreeable woman on earth.

12:12.700 --> 12:20.420
When suddenly three boy scouts rushed around the corner and almost knocked her over, she did not

12:20.420 --> 12:26.640
condemn the boy scouts, but immediately called on the law of forgiveness and saluted the divinity

12:26.640 --> 12:34.060
in the woman. Wisdom's ways are ways of pleasantness, and all her paths are peace.

12:35.080 --> 12:40.880
When one has made his demands upon the universal, he must be ready for surprises.

12:41.600 --> 12:47.760
Everything may seem to be going wrong, when in reality it is going right. For example,

12:48.180 --> 12:54.800
a woman was told that there was no loss in divine mind, therefore she could not lose anything which

12:54.800 --> 13:03.320
belonged to her. Anything lost would be returned, or she would receive its equivalent. Several years

13:03.320 --> 13:10.100
previously she had lost $2,000. She had loaned the money to a relative during her lifetime,

13:10.100 --> 13:17.620
but the relative had died, leaving no mention of it in her will. The woman was resentful and angry,

13:18.020 --> 13:23.200
and as she had no written statement of the transaction, she never received the money,

13:23.540 --> 13:30.060
so she determined to deny the loss and collect the $2,000 from the bank of the universal.

13:30.860 --> 13:37.220
She had to begin by forgiving the woman, as resentment and unforgiveness closed the door

13:37.220 --> 13:44.360
of this wonderful bank. She made this statement, I deny loss, there is no loss in divine mind,

13:44.560 --> 13:52.740
therefore I cannot lose the $2,000 which belonged to me by divine right. As one door shuts, another

13:52.740 --> 14:00.100
opens. She was living in an apartment house, which was for sale, and in the lease was a clause,

14:00.540 --> 14:05.580
stating that if the house was sold, the tenants would be required to move out within 90 days.

14:06.220 --> 14:13.140
Suddenly the landlord broke the leases and raised the rent. Again injustice was on her pathway,

14:13.500 --> 14:17.920
but this time she was undisturbed. She blessed the landlord and said,

14:18.420 --> 14:24.400
as the rent has been raised, it means that I'll be that much richer, for God is my supply.

14:26.700 --> 14:33.440
The new leases were made out for the advanced rent, but by some divine mistake the 90-day

14:33.440 --> 14:39.700
clause had been forgotten. Soon after, the landlord had an opportunity to sell the house.

14:40.200 --> 14:45.360
On account of the mistake in the new leases, the tenants held possession for another year.

14:46.260 --> 14:52.420
The agent offered each tenant $200 if he would vacate. Several families moved,

14:53.080 --> 14:59.440
three remained, including the woman. A month or two passed, and the agent again appeared.

14:59.440 --> 15:04.360
This time he said to the woman, will you break your lease for the sum of $1,500?

15:05.460 --> 15:12.220
It flashed upon her, here comes the $2,000. She remembered having said to friends in the house,

15:13.060 --> 15:18.720
we will all act together if anything more is said about leaving. So her lead was to consult her

15:18.720 --> 15:25.660
friends. These friends said, well, if they have offered you $1,500, they will certainly give $2,000.

15:26.290 --> 15:32.320
So she received a check for $2,000 for giving up the apartment. It was certainly a remarkable

15:32.320 --> 15:38.320
working of the law, and the apparent injustice was merely an opening for the way for her

15:38.320 --> 15:47.820
demonstration. It proved that there is no loss, and when man takes his spiritual stand,

15:48.320 --> 15:52.620
he collects all that is his from this great reservoir of good.

15:54.520 --> 15:58.800
I will restore to you the years the locusts have eaten.

15:59.680 --> 16:06.540
The locusts are the doubts, fears, resentments, and regrets of mortal thinking. These adverse

16:06.540 --> 16:14.580
thoughts alone rob man, for no man gives to himself but himself, and no man takes away from

16:14.580 --> 16:22.240
himself but himself. Man is here to prove God and to bear witness to the truth,

16:22.880 --> 16:29.520
and he can only prove God by bringing plenty out of lack and justice out of injustice.

16:30.680 --> 16:38.380
Prove me now herewith, saith the Lord of hosts, if I will not open you the windows of heaven

16:38.380 --> 16:43.320
and pour out a blessing, that there shall be not room enough to receive it.

16:44.580 --> 16:49.020
End of chapter 8. Recording by Amy Conger.

